Dear Raffaella,

Recordings and Documents

We refer to your request for your personal information related to your clai=
m. Some content has been withheld/redacted as they contain the personal inf=
ormation of another party - Sec 53(b)  or they are protected by commercial =
sensitive information - Sec 52(1).

If you believe any of the personal information held by Tower is incorrect, =
you have the right to request a correction under the Privacy Act 2020.

If you have any further questions or concerns, please contact us on 0800 80=
8 808.

