break-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Dear Raffaella,<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b>Recordings and Documents</b><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">We refer to your request for your personal informati=
on related to your claim. Some content has been withheld/redacted as they c=
ontain the personal information of another party &#8211; Sec 53(b) &nbsp;or=
 they are protected by commercial sensitive information
 &#8211; Sec 52(1).<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">If you believe any of the personal information held =
by Tower is incorrect, you have the right to request a correction under the=
 Privacy Act 2020.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">If you have any further questions or concerns, pleas=
e contact us on 0800 808 808.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Please use the link below to get access <o:p></o:p><=
/p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><a href=3D"https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-sb536b89e=
04b44cfb80c62fbda4f2e9c0">https://towernz.sharefile.com/d-sb536b89e04b44cfb=
80c62fbda4f2e9c0</a><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">Warm regards<o:p></o:p></p>
